Patrick Johnstone will be the referee and emcee, but the real stars of this walk will be the candidates who have already agreed to attend (all times below are approximate!):
 Judy Darcy of the BC NDP will address the crowd at 5:35pm at Sapprton Park;
Hector Bremner of the BC Liberals will address the crowd at 6:00pm at the BC Pen Steps;
James Crosty  Independant Candidates will address the crowd at 6:15 at Victoria Hill; 
Terry Teather  of the BC Green Party will address the cowd at 6:35pm at Albert Crescent Park;
Paul Forseth of the BC Conservatives will address the crowd 7:00pm at Hyack Square.

